data.description: **Price Reduced 1-20-2024** We are featuring a spacious home is situated in the outskirts of the City of San Jacinto near Ramona Expressway with beautiful mountain views. This home was built in 2018 and features many amenities including an above ground swimming pool. From the moment you drive up to your future home, you will notice how tastefully upgraded this property is. This 4-bedroom 2 bath home offers over 2100 sqft of living space that sits a huge 9500+ sqft Lot w/ possible RV access. As you enter the home you will notice the large great room area. The floors have been fully upgraded with premium flooring throughout the entire home. The beautiful kitchen is equipped with granite counter tops and is completely open with an enormous granite countertop center island, white cabinets with so much extra storage, upgraded appliances, stainless steel deep sink with decorative lighting over the island. Home also has a walk-in pantry with the large family room and dining area for entertainment... Master bedroom is very spacious with a barn door leading into the bathroom with a very large walk-in closet. The other 3 bedrooms are also very spacious. Wait to see the backyard talk about an entertainer’s paradise that has a newer outdoor pool to enjoy for those hot summer days. Backyard also features a alum wood patio deck with two upgraded fans, and an entertainment area to watch the big screen TV… Home come with paid off builder installed solar panels. This home also has a Tankless water heater, a water softener (negotiable) along with a 2-car garage... This Home is located at the end of a cul-de-sac street. Way too many other features to mention... Owners spared no cost Lots of attention to detail!! Nothing but the best products were used in remodeling. GREAT FOR FIRST-TIME HOME BUYERS! DON’T MISS OUT! ABSOLUTELY NO HOA! TURNKEY & PRIDE OF OWNERSHIP. MOVE IN READY. AND MUST SEE TO TRULY APPRECIATE!!
